<i>I can tell</i>
<i>by the tone of your voice</i>

46:29.521 --> 46:31.220
<i>something's wrong.</i>
<i>What's wrong?</i>

46:33.558 --> 46:35.391
<i>There's this guy</i>
<i>I'm working with.</i>

46:35.393 --> 46:36.926
<i>Can't really talk specifics,</i>

46:36.928 --> 46:41.097
<i>but I think he's makin'</i>
<i>a big mistake.</i>

46:41.099 --> 46:42.765
<i>Can you get him</i>
<i>to change his mind?</i>

46:44.068 --> 46:46.035
<i>I'm tryin',</i>
<i>but he's a stubborn one.</i>

46:47.539 --> 46:48.538
<i>Well, you've been known</i>

46:48.540 --> 46:50.807
<i>to have the power</i>
<i>of persuasion.</i>

46:50.809 --> 46:54.143
<i>Yeah, well, we'll see.</i>

46:54.145 --> 46:55.411
<i>I got to get goin'.</i>

46:55.413 --> 46:58.347
