47:30.248 --> 47:32.014
Let's just hang together.

47:33.151 --> 47:34.584
- No.

47:34.586 --> 47:36.719
Ladies, how's the wine?

47:36.721 --> 47:39.021
- Not bad.
- Can't complain.

47:39.023 --> 47:41.557
- Yeah? You-you visiting
from out of town?

47:41.559 --> 47:43.025
- No, I live here in Carmel.

47:43.027 --> 47:45.428
She's in town
visiting from Berkeley.

47:45.430 --> 47:47.597
- Cool. I'm Wes.

47:47.599 --> 47:48.931
- Rebecca.
- Ellen.

47:48.933 --> 47:50.867
- Very good to meet you.
I don't mean to be a creep,

47:50.869 --> 47:53.035
but do you see this scruffy guy,
over here?

47:53.037 --> 47:54.036
Hmm-mm.

47:54.038 --> 47:55.905
This guy
is a dear friend of mine,

47:55.907 --> 47:58.674
and a troubled-- a troubled man,
and um, here's the deal.

47:58.676 --> 47:59.742
Here's what I think
we should do.

47:59.744 --> 48:02.078
The four of us
should go to dinner.

48:02.080 --> 48:05.047
Some good food,
some adult conversations.

48:05.049 --> 48:07.183
A couple of drinks,
maybe several drinks.

48:07.185 --> 48:10.486
Just take some time to remind
ourselves of life's joys

48:10.488 --> 48:14.223
and in so doing, we can help
this poor Sad Sack over here

48:14.225 --> 48:16.492
