49:07.612 --> 49:12.081
We could totally go back
to some hotel room

49:12.083 --> 49:15.084
and um, sleep together.
- Hmm.

49:15.086 --> 49:16.552
- Hmm.
- Mm.

49:16.554 --> 49:18.821
