meant to be together.

50:54.185 --> 50:56.118
Best of luck to both of you--

50:56.120 --> 50:57.887
- Thank you.
- --On that tragic journey.

50:59.123 --> 51:01.323
Rebecca, how about you?

51:01.325 --> 51:02.792
- Ha. Uh...

51:02.794 --> 51:06.495
