I signed my divorce papers.

51:29.053 --> 51:30.419
- Sorry to hear that.

51:31.923 --> 51:33.189
- It's okay.

51:36.227 --> 51:37.226
Actually...

51:39.197 --> 51:42.398
it feels good to say it.

51:42.400 --> 51:44.366
Yeah.

51:44.368 --> 51:45.901
I'm divorced.

51:48.739 --> 51:49.705
- There you go.

51:49.707 --> 51:51.574
- Hmm.

51:51.576 --> 51:53.676
- It's why I came down.

51:53.678 --> 51:54.844
Just to give her some support

51:54.846 --> 51:57.513
