closed the chapter.

51:59.150 --> 52:01.150
Look at the sunset,
have a drink.

52:01.152 --> 52:03.018
Think about a new chapter.

52:04.222 --> 52:06.288
Come on.
To a new beginning.

52:15.833 --> 52:17.166
- What about you, Wes?

52:18.503 --> 52:20.202
- Uhm.

52:20.204 --> 52:21.303
Well...

52:22.373 --> 52:23.639
I'm married.

52:23.641 --> 52:24.707
- Hmm.

52:24.709 --> 52:26.475
- We have a baby girl.

52:26.477 --> 52:28.577
